article.story: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. -- — Shahada Wells' 36 points led McNeese over UAB 81-60 on Tuesday night. Wells also had six rebounds and three blocks for the Cowboys (6-2). Antavion Collum scored 20 points, going 8 of 13 (4 for 7 from 3-point range). Daniel Ortiz led the way for the Blazers (4-3) with 20 points. Eric Gaines added eight points for UAB. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
